Changed paths:
 M http://src.chromium.org/viewvc/chrome/trunk/src/native_client/tools/modular-build/build.py?r1=4581&amp;r2=4580&amp;pathrev=4581
 M http://src.chromium.org/viewvc/chrome/trunk/src/native_client/SConstruct?r1=4581&amp;r2=4580&amp;pathrev=4581
 M http://src.chromium.org/viewvc/chrome/trunk/src/native_client/tools/modular-build/treemappers.py?r1=4581&amp;r2=4580&amp;pathrev=4581

Add dynamic_library_browser_tests to be run on Buildbot

Add "browser_headless" Scons option for running the browser through
Xvfb (a headless X11 display) on Linux.  This is easier than launching
VNC in a separate build step and will be useful for general
development testing too.

Add "chrome_binaries_dir" Scons option so that downloaded files do not
have to be placed within the source tree (since modular-build tries to
separate source/build dirs).

